## Getting Started

### Add repository

```bash
helm repo add {{ template "chart.name" . }} https://example.com/helm-charts
helm repo update
```

### Install

```bash
helm install my-{{ template "chart.name" . }} {{ template "chart.name" . }}/{{ template "chart.name" . }} \
  --namespace {{ template "chart.name" . }} \
  --create-namespace
```

### Upgrade

```bash
